<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>Калашников: эволюция легенды</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: #0B0E11;
            color: #fff;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            scroll-behavior: smooth;
        }

        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');

        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(30px);
            }
            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        @keyframes glowPulse {
            0% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3); }
            70% { box-shadow: 0 0 20px 10px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1); }
            100% { box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3); }
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1400px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 0 40px;
        }

        .header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            z-index: 1000;
            background: rgba(11, 14, 17, 0.9);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            padding: 20px 0;
        }

        .header .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 800;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #d32f2f 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .nav {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .nav a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: 0.3s;
            position: relative;
        }

        .nav a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            background: #d32f2f;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .nav a:hover {
            color: #fff;
        }

        .nav a:hover::after {
            width: 100%;
        }

        .hero {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 30% 50%, #1a2329 0%, #0B0E11 70%);
            padding: 100px 0;
        }

        .hero-bg {
            position: absolute;
            right: 0;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            width: 60%;
            height: 80%;
            background: url('https://avatars.mds.yandex.net/get-entity_search/2394172/1040570462/S600xU_2x') no-repeat right center;
            background-size: contain;
            opacity: 0.1;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: fadeInUp 1s ease;
        }

        .hero-label {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 30px;
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 72px;
            font-weight: 800;
            line-height: 1.1;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .hero h1 span {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d32f2f, #ff8a80);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
        }

        .hero-stats {
            display: flex;
            gap: 60px;
        }

        .stat-item {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .stat-number {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #d32f2f;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .stat-label {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            font-size: 16px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 100px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
            position: relative;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .section-title::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -15px;
            left: 0;
            width: 80px;
            height: 4px;
            background: #d32f2f;
            border-radius: 2px;
        }

        .context-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 40px;
            margin-bottom: 60px;
        }

        .context-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: 0.5s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .context-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 100% 0%, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1), transparent 70%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }

        .context-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4);
        }

        .context-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .context-icon {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .context-card h3 {
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .context-card p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .context-card .weakness {
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .timeline {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            position: relative;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .timeline-item:hover {
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
            border-color: #d32f2f;
        }

        .timeline-year {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .timeline-desc {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .bio {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 60px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .bio-image {
            position: relative;
        }

        .bio-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 30px;
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .bio-quote {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -30px;
            right: -30px;
            background: #d32f2f;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            max-width: 300px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-style: italic;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
        }

        .bio-quote-author {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-style: normal;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .bio-text h3 {
            font-size: 36px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .bio-text p {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .bio-principle {
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
            border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 10px 10px 0;
        }

        .weapon-showcase {
            display: grid;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .weapon-card {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            transition: 0.5s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .weapon-card::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at 0% 100%, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1), transparent 70%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }

        .weapon-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px) scale(1.01);
            border-color: #d32f2f;
            box-shadow: 0 30px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        }

        .weapon-card:hover::before {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .weapon-image {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 20px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .weapon-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            transition: 0.5s;
            max-height: 300px;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        .weapon-card:hover .weapon-image img {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .weapon-info h3 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #d32f2f;
        }

        .weapon-desc {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7);
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .weapon-specs {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .spec {
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .spec-label {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            font-size: 14px;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .spec-value {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .weapon-feature {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
            border: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 30px;
            color: #d32f2f;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-right: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .compare-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .compare-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 30px;
            padding: 40px;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }

        .compare-card:hover {
            border-color: #d32f2f;
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
        }

        .compare-card h3 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .compare-card:first-child h3 {
            color: #d32f2f;
        }

        .compare-card:last-child h3 {
            color: #3a6ea5;
        }

        .compare-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 15px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .compare-label {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
        }

        .compare-value {
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .compare-highlight {
            background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
        }

        .factors-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .factor-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1), transparent);
            border: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            transition: 0.5s;
        }

        .factor-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-color: #d32f2f;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2);
            animation: glowPulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .factor-number {
            font-size: 48px;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: #d32f2f;
            opacity: 0.3;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .factor-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .factor-desc {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.6);
        }

        .conclusion {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.2), transparent);
            border: 2px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);
            border-radius: 40px;
            padding: 60px;
            margin: 60px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .conclusion::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('https://img.kalashnikovgroup.ru/1400x475,fit/https://cdn.kalashnikovgroup.ru/static/images/3/8/i/38i1304-15508-1080.jpg') no-repeat center;
            background-size: cover;
            opacity: 0.03;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .conclusion h2 {
            font-size: 48px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            color: #d32f2f;
            position: relative;
        }

        .conclusion p {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
            position: relative;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .conclusion-quote {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-style: italic;
            color: #d32f2f;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 40px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .footer {
            padding: 60px 0;
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        .footer-content {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .footer-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
        }

        .footer-links a {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .footer-links a:hover {
            color: #d32f2f;
        }

        /* ========== АДАПТИВ ДЛЯ ТЕЛЕФОНОВ (ИСПРАВЛЕН) ========== */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                padding: 0 20px;
            }
            
            .hero {
                min-height: auto;
                padding: 120px 0 60px;
            }
            
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 36px;
                line-height: 1.2;
            }
            
            .hero p {
                font-size: 16px;
                margin-bottom: 30px;
            }
            
            .hero-stats {
                gap: 25px;
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .stat-number {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .stat-label {
                font-size: 12px;
            }
            
            .hero-bg {
                position: relative;
                width: 100%;
                height: 200px;
                opacity: 0.2;
                margin-top: 30px;
                background-size: contain;
                background-position: center;
                top: auto;
                transform: none;
            }
            
            .hero-content {
                text-align: center;
                max-width: 100%;
            }
            
            .hero-stats {
                justify-content: center;
            }
            
            .stat-item {
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .context-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            
            .bio {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 40px;
            }
            
            .bio-quote {
                position: relative;
                bottom: 0;
                right: 0;
                margin-top: 20px;
                max-width: 100%;
                padding: 20px;
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .weapon-card {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                padding: 25px;
                gap: 25px;
            }
            
            .weapon-info h3 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .weapon-desc {
                font-size: 16px;
            }
            
            .weapon-specs {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            }
            
            .spec-value {
                font-size: 20px;
            }
            
            .compare-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 30px;
            }
            
            .compare-card {
                padding: 30px;
            }
            
            .factors-grid {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            
            .timeline {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                gap: 15px;
            }
            
            .section-title {
                font-size: 32px;
                margin-bottom: 40px;
            }
            
            .section {
                padding: 60px 0;
            }
            
            .conclusion {
                padding: 30px;
                margin: 40px 0;
            }
            
            .conclusion h2 {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
            
            .conclusion p {
                font-size: 16px;
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .conclusion-quote {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .nav {
                display: none;
            }
            
            .footer-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 20px;
                text-align: center;
            }
            
            .footer-links {
                flex-wrap: wrap;
                justify-content: center;
                gap: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <header class="header">
        <div class="container">
            <a href="#" class="logo">КАЛАШНИКОВ</a>
            <nav class="nav">
                <a href="#context">Контекст</a>
                <a href="#bio">Биография</a>
                <a href="#ak47">АК-47</a>
                <a href="#evolution">Эволюция</a>
                <a href="#compare">Сравнение</a>
                <a href="#factors">Факторы успеха</a>
            </nav>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-bg"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="hero-content">
                <span class="hero-label">1919 — 2013</span>
                <h1>Человек,<br>изменивший <span>оружие</span></h1>
                <p>Михаил Калашников создал не просто автомат. Он создал технический феномен, ставший символом эпохи и эталоном надежности для всего мира.</p>
                <div class="hero-stats">
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">>100 млн</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">выпущено</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">>70 лет</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">на вооружении</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="stat-item">
                        <div class="stat-number">>100 стран</div>
                        <div class="stat-label">используют</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="context">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Почему мир ждал новый автомат?</h2>
            <div class="context-grid">
                <div class="context-card">
                    <div class="context-icon">🔫</div>
                    <h3>Винтовки</h3>
                    <p>Точные на больших дистанциях, но громоздкие и медленные. Каждый выстрел требует ручной перезарядки. Пример: винтовка Мосина ("трёхлинейка").</p>
                    <div class="weakness">Главный недостаток: низкая скорострельность в ближнем бою</div>
                </div>
                <div class="context-card">
                    <div class="context-icon">⚡</div>
                    <h3>Пистолеты-пулемёты</h3>
                    <p>Могут стрелять очередями, компактны, но используют слабый пистолетный патрон. Эффективны только до 150 метров. Пример: ППШ.</p>
                    <div class="weakness">Главный недостаток: слабая пуля, низкая точность на средней дистанции</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center; margin: 60px 0; background: rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.1); padding: 40px; border-radius: 30px; border: 1px solid rgba(211, 47, 47, 0.3);">
                <p style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 20px;">Решение: промежуточный патрон</p>
                <p style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.7); font-size: 18px;">Слабее винтовочного, но мощнее пистолетного. Позволил создать автомат — оружие для средней дистанции (200-400 м).</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">1944</div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">StG-44</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Первый в мире автомат (Германия)</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">1947</div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">АК-47</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Победа в конкурсе</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-year">1949</div>
                    <div class="timeline-title">Принятие на вооружение</div>
                    <div class="timeline-desc">Начало легенды</div>
                </div>
